Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.93,Karaoke_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,375)}... kono mune ni yakitsuita...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:22.86,Karaoke_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,375)}... mabushii egao.
